Git-LibGit2 version 0.01
========================

This module is an experiment to see if wrapping Libgit2 but presenting
a Git::PurePerl-like API to it is a good idea.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires the libgit2 library installed first.

  git clone git://github.com/libgit2/libgit2.git
  cd libgit2
  ./waf configure
  ./waf build-shared
  ./waf test
  sudo ./waf install

